This is Impatience, a card Solitaire / Patience implementation for Perl/SDL
by FROGGS and Shlomi Fish.

Currently it only implements Klondike ( 
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Klondike_%28solitaire%29 ), without any numbered
deals.

For more information about Perl/SDL see http://sdl.perl.org/ .

More information about Patience and card Solitaire can be found at:

* http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patience_%28game%29

* http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Category:Solitaire_card_games

* http://pysolfc.sourceforge.net/ - PySolFC, a comprehensive open source 
implementation in Python using Tkinter.

